{"tid":1679115,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上環禧利街凌晨cafe 示威者避難所","createTime":"2019-10-28T04:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T12:59:14.000Z","uid":202798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39f5d1b8cce7cddb281858e40f4d4a2b846d983d","tid":1679115,"uid":202798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191028/60194596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F60194596&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5wTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=01cacb05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F60194596&h=9b9e3d3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191028/60194596</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bz7VzMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbz7VzMN.jpg&h=babd0ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PL9kLTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPL9kLTu.jpg&h=e07f225c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/28/121059_eb608e8102941763b70c7a45dd6c1921.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F28%2F121059_eb608e8102941763b70c7a45dd6c1921.jpeg&h=92883efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1aiJJE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1aiJJE1.jpg&h=65e487f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人說，我們的城市在回歸前後，不過是暫借的土壤，是「借來的地方，借來的時間」。夾縫裏自由的空氣，或許是海市蜃樓。這城裏的核心繁華地段，上環禧利街，有處地方，每晚亦恍如經歷一段「借來的時間」。<br />\n<br />\n這間小店日間時段叫Why 50，深宵時段叫Night Owl，亦即「夜鳥」，開至凌晨三點，成了一班無心睡眠的人的咖啡窩。全港島區，僅此一間。<br />\n<br />\n這小店本來就叫Why 50，已有九年沖咖啡經驗的老闆阿逸，在四年前開業，一邊做咖啡培訓師；至今年三月，Mandi向阿逸提議，讓他做黃昏至凌晨的時段。兩人才見面兩次，這小靈感便實現起來。阿逸指：「當時一個月裏只有幾天開到凌晨。試了幾天，我問是不是繼續？他答，繼續吧，便一直到現在。我們做咖啡的，十個有十個的夢想，便是開一家咖啡店。我自己有幸開這間咖啡店，會不會能夠讓這個地方，令其他人做到同樣的事情呢？」<br />\n<br />\n夜間話事人Mandi，日間正職在機場工作，同事多數為藍絲或對時事議題較冷漠的。「礙於我公司的立場和身邊同事的看法，我處於好壓抑的狀態。每次發生特別大的事情，例如是爆眼、中槍，我總會帶着好負面的心情回去上班。同事們甚至會罵示威者作暴徒，最可笑是說警察搜查被捕人士的家時，發現他們床下收起了一篋美金，但追根究柢，原來只是他們聽聞回來。」"},{"pid":"7419fca04ac720d06ddf651199646ddda82e3a8a","tid":1679115,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e8efc64431b4dce9ef39bf388f8265c889f31dec","tid":1679115,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"返兩份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0390de053052f523d6c16094efa91cb2acfae5ca","tid":1679115,"uid":293848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8efc64431b4dce9ef39bf388f8265c889f31dec","tid":1679115,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"返兩份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"又係爆肝追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}